{"tid":2172451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇籲做好準備才放寬防疫措施","createTime":"2020-08-24T15:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:18:12.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de6b4f9aa9137e0886c699e4e3fe590a07f82ac9","tid":2172451,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"袁國勇籲做好準備才放寬防疫措施<br />\n2020-08-24 HKT 22:53<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......袁國勇認為，確診宗數能夠回落至單位數，如果放鬆防疫措施，尤其重開食肆卻沒有足夠準備，疫情有機會反彈。至於現時有無條件放寬二人限聚令、限制食肆等防疫措施，他說最重要是做好準備才放寬。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，食肆方面，一定要分開傳菜與執枱工作，因為負責執枱的員工會接觸到食客沾有口水、甚至有病毒的碗碟，若同一人負責執枱及傳菜，可引起嚴重交叉感染......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545623-20200824.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545623-20200824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=51d18383\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545623-20200824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3aa08df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545623-20200824.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">我就已做好準備在放寬防疫措施後狂歡</span></strong></span>"}]}